the first review/kagemusha well , this is the first time for a review , and i was recomended to this review . so here it goes.first of all wow ! ! ! i mean wooow what a score , bear mccreary did a hell of a job on this project . its like a mix of all kinds of composers , like harry gregson williams ( from man on fire ) , halo lot of cue`s , i could go on , and ofcause a danish group called safri duo . if anyone of your guys and girls like this kind of sumption , then buy it now